quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,61,Ababaka bwe baatuuka awali abantu ba (Nabbi) Luutu
  15,62,(Luutu) naagamba nti mazima mmwe muli abantu abatamanyidddwa
  15,63,"Nebagamba nti: ssi ekyo kyokka wabula tukujjidde n'ekyo kye baali babuusabuusa"
  15,64,"Era tukuleetedde amazima, era ddala ffe bye twogera bituufu"
  15,65,"Kale tambula n'abantubo mu kitundu ky'ekiro era (ggwe) baveeko emabega tewaba omu ku mmwe akyuka, era mugende eyo gye mulagiddwa"
  15,66,Netumuwa ekiragiro nti abasembayo ku bo baakuggwawo nga busaasaana
  15,67,Abantu bo mu kibuga nebajja (ewa Luutu) nga bafa essanyu (olw'abagenyi abavubuka abaali bakyaddeyo)
  15,68,(Luutu) naagamba nti mazima abo bemulaba bagenyi bange temunsonyiwaza
  15,69,Era mutye Katonda temunswaza
  15,70,"Nebagamba nti: abaffe tetwakugaana (okuleeta wano) abantu"
  15,71,Naabagamba nti bawala bange baabo bwe muba nga mulina kukikola
  15,72,"(Katonda agamba nti) ndayidde obulamu bwo (ggwe Muhammad) mazima bo mu kukola ebyo byonna, baali babuyaanira mu butamiivu bwabwe"
  15,73,Okubwatuka (okwamaanyi) nekubatuukako nga enjuba evaayo
  15,74,"(Netuvuunika ebyalo byabwe) netuzza waggulu waabyo wansi, netubafukirira amayinja ag'o mu bbumba eryokye"
  15,75,Mazima mu ebyo mulimu obubonero eri abo abalondoozi b'obubonero
  15,76,Era mazima ebyalo ebyo (ebyazikirizibwa) biri ku kkubo erikyaliwo (agendayo asobola okubiraba)
  15,77,Mazima mu ebyo mulimu akabonero (akalaga obusobozi bwa Katonda) eri abakkiriza
  15,78,Era mazima n'abantu b'omukibira baali beeyisa bubi
  15,79,Netubazikiriza era mazima abantu ab'emirundi ebiri (aba Luutu ne Swaibu) baali ku kkubo erimanyiddwa (buli ayitawo alabawo)